dcterms:description: A comprehensive benchmark dataset of surround view images collected from various indoor and outdoor parking sites, representing diverse real-world scenarios. The dataset comprises three distinct categories of parking spots: Regular, Handicap, and Electric-Vehicle (EV). It includes 1352 generated bird’s eye view images with a total of 11,505 labels distributed across these categories.
dcterms:title: Parking Slot Detection and Classification Dataset
